WEBVTT

00:00:59.758 --> 00:01:01.600
These essential fatty acids,

00:01:01.600 --> 00:01:05.045
which have been linked to preventing
degenerative brain conditions,

00:01:05.045 --> 00:01:07.256
must come from our diets.

00:01:07.256 --> 00:01:09.005
So eating omega-rich foods,

00:01:09.005 --> 00:01:09.827
like nuts,

00:01:09.827 --> 00:01:10.651
seeds,

00:01:10.651 --> 00:01:11.944
and fatty fish,

00:01:11.944 --> 00:01:16.755
is crucial to the creation and maintenance
of cell membranes.

00:01:16.755 --> 00:01:19.320
And while omegas are good fats
for your brain,

00:01:19.320 --> 00:01:23.918
long-term consumption of other fats,
like trans and saturated fats,

00:01:23.918 --> 00:01:26.601
may compromise brain health.

